### Parte 2: Prompts para Generaci￳n de Im￡genes (IA)

Para mantener la consistencia visual (estilo Tron/Game Boy/Big Hero 6), cada prompt debe incluir el "Estilo Base" al final. He traducido tu guion a prompts optimizados para herramientas como Midjourney o DALL-E 3.

**Estilo Base (A￱adir al final de cada prompt):**
> `... in the style of Tron legacy, retro arcade graphics, Big Hero 6 clean technology, Sims UI elements, mint green color palette, high gloss, 8k resolution, 16:9 aspect ratio.`

**Los 20 Prompts:**

1.  **Comando Celestial:** Pure white bright background. A single neon green pixel (#98FF98) blinking in the exact center. Retro arcade font appearing letter by letter spelling "heaven_on_earth.exe".
2.  **El Inventario (Las P￭ldoras):** Background transforms into a subtle digital grid. Three floating pill icons with a bouncy elastic animation. They look like video game power-ups, glowing mint green.
3.  **La Mano Digital:** Abstract background of soft pastel geometric shapes. A hand made of vector lines and wireframes entering from the right side, offering the glowing pills.
4.  **La Dilataci￳n (Asombro):** Close-up of a character named Jensen. Relaxed face, conspiratorial smile, eyes wide open in "Wow". Reflection in eyes shows a spinning world filling with mint green color.
5.  **La Magia del Humo Menta:** Jensen takes a green pill. It dissolves into sparkling mint green smoke. The smoke looks like digital confetti, glittering, "computer magic".
6.  **El ￁tomo Feliz:** Entire environment turns mint green. Jensen is now a giant observing a single atom. The atom has a cute smiling face. Jensen touches it and the atom bounces with joy.
7.  **La Mol￩cula Lego:** Happy atoms joining together. They form structures resembling Lego blocks. Building themselves quickly and perfectly, mint green and pastel colors.
8.  **La C￩lula Vital:** Structures turn into a giant transparent cell. Inside the cell, the nucleus glows like a small sun. A perfect, self-contained ecosystem.
9.  **El ￓrgano Musical:** Cells form a pulsing heart or brain. Each beat sends waves of color and visualized music. Jensen floats on top of this organ, surfing the light waves.
10. **El Organismo / El Avatar:** Zoom out. The heart is part of a human body made of light and circuits. Idealized, healthy, powerful version of a human. Jensen gives a high-five to this glowing giant figure.
11. **La Comunidad (Sims Style):** Many light-beings appear. They greet each other, collaborate. Floating chat bubbles with "like" icons and happy emojis. Mint green interaction UI.
12. **La Sociedad (Ciudad Futurista):** Communities form a futuristic city. Buildings growing like plants, flying cars that are soft data capsules. No traffic, just harmonious flow. Big Hero 6 aesthetic.
13. **El Planeta Joya:** The city is part of a continent, part of a planet. The planet looks like a shiny marble. Jensen floats in space viewing a healthy, radiant Earth.
14. **El Universo en Condensaci￳n:** Earth is part of a solar system, which is a giant molecule in a galaxy. The universe spins fast and implodes gently inward. Galaxies becoming planets, becoming cells, becoming atoms.
15. **La P￭ldora de Nuevo:** The immense universe condenses into a single bright point: The Mint Green Pill floating in front of Jensen again. Text concept: "Everything is connected".
16. **El Nacimiento de las Alas:** Jensen holds the pill. Wings burst from his back with a flash of white light. Not classic angel wings, but technological crystal wings with feathers of light.
17. **El Vuello (Peter Pan Digital):** Infinite blue sky, soft digital painting clouds. Jensen flies in a superhero pose (Iron Man style), elegant and graceful. Total smile, absolute freedom. Arms open receiving digital wind.
18. **Punto en el Horizonte:** Jensen flying away, becoming smaller. Leaving a trail of fairy dust / mint green powder. Becoming a tiny bright dot on the horizon line where sky meets sea.
19. **El Pixel Final:** The dot zooms back to the camera. Becomes pixelated. Turns into a perfect square Mint Green Pixel. Centered, minimalist, clean.
20. **Logo y Lanzamiento:** Clean white or black background. The Pixel morphs smoothly into a logo featuring wings. Text animates "SAVE THE WORLD" and "launching.exe...". A blinking cursor at the end.

